name: Thermolt
pokedex: It regulates convection currents beneath the earth's surface. Its metal body is partially melted by its own heat.

name: Wattrel
pokedex: When its wings catch the wind, the bones within produce electricity. This Pokémon dives into the ocean, catching prey by electrocuting them.

name: GRD Barbaracle
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Regirock. Pieces of its loathesome, rugged body chip off and impede its enemies.

name: Kilowattrel
pokedex: Kilowattrel inflates its throat sac to amplify its electricity. By riding the wind, this Pokémon can fly over 430 miles in a day.

name: G-Weezing
pokedex: This Pokémon consumes particles that contaminate the air. Instead of leaving droppings, it expels clean air.

name: Gritagonist
pokedex: Gather your party! The fearless leader of this quest, Gritagonist heroically fights for its friends no matter the odds!

name: Rivivory
pokedex: Gather your party! The healer of this quest, Rivivory tends to every need of the others, be it physical, mental, or spiritual!

name: Persebony
pokedex: Gather your party! The mage of this quest, Persebony's insight, knowledge, and diverse magics will be needed at every turn!

name: Wardraide
pokedex: Gather your party! The muscle of this quest, Wardraide brings valuable connections and serious brawn to any encounter!

name: Barralvo
pokedex: Gather your party! The warrior of this quest, Barralvo is here to have a blast--with lots of laughing and explosions!

name: Familiore
pokedex: Gather your party! The specialist of this quest, Familiore is funny, quirky, and unique! Who knows what it may have in store!

name: Tantamat
pokedex: Gather your party! The rogue of this quest, don't let Tantamat's bag of tricks and lethal precision take you by surprise!

name: GRD Girafarig
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Raikou. The rapidity of its flashing movements causes bouts of seizures.

name: Knitterbug
pokedex: Surprisingly durable for having a cloth exoskeleton, this cute specter pretends to be a plush doll before surprise attacking prey.

name: Crawstitch
pokedex: No one knows what it looks like beneath its endless layers of cloth. If you ever fully unravel it, it will suck out your very soul!

name: Destineedle
pokedex: It thrives in cold, dark environments. After incapacitating prey, it sews its helpless victims into caricatures which decorate its lair.

name: Ankylure
pokedex: Lying beneath loose sand or mud, they bait unsuspecting prey to their demise. The nodes on its carapace are not defensive but rather work as barometers.

name: Farfarato
pokedex: Farfarato's wings capture stories of their trainers like photographs, tinting the memories based on whether or not it remembers them fondly.

name: Calyrex
pokedex: Calyrex is known in legend as a king that ruled over places uninhabited by humans. It has the power to cause hearts to mend and plants to spring forth.

name: G-Slowpoke
pokedex: Although this Pokémon is normally zoned out, its expression abruptly sharpens on occasion. The cause for this seems to lie in Slowpoke's diet.

name: G-Slowbro
pokedex: If this Pokémon squeezes the tongue of the shell on its arm, it will launch a toxic liquid from the tip of its shell.

name: G-Slowking
pokedex: While chanting strange spells, this Pokémon combines its internal toxins with what it's eaten, creating strange concoctions.

name: Lechonk
pokedex: It possesses a keen sense of smell but doesn't use it for anything other than foraging. It makes an excellent spit roast.

name: Oinkologne
pokedex: This meticulous Pokémon only uses mud for spa treatments. It even shrouds itself in a floral aroma that soothes the Pokémon around it.

name: Nymble
pokedex: It has its third set of legs folded up. When it's in a tough spot, this Pokémon jumps over 30 feet using the strength of its legs.

name: Lokix
pokedex: When it decides to fight all out, it stands on its previously folded legs. It neutralizes its enemies in short order.

name: Pawmot
pokedex: This Pokémon is incredibly quick to react, happy to enter battle and then strike down enemies with lightning-fast movements.

name: Tandemaus
pokedex: Exhibiting great teamwork, they use their incisors to cut pieces out of any material that might be useful for a nest, then make off with them.

name: Maushold
pokedex: They build huge nests with many rooms that are used for different purposes, such as eating, playing, and sleeping.

name: Fidough
pokedex: This Pokémon is smooth and moist to the touch. Yeast in Fidough's breath induces misty fermentation in the Pokémon's vicinity.

name: Fuedough
pokedex: When exposed to heat, this Pokémon's skin shimmers and yields an appetizing aroma. Otherwise, hope you like the smell of fermenting yeast!

name: Nacli
pokedex: It was born in a layer of rock salt deep under the earth. This species was particularly treasured in the old days, as they would share precious salt.

name: Naclstack
pokedex: It compresses rock salt inside its body and shoots out hardened salt pellets with enough force to perforate an iron sheet.

name: Garganacl
pokedex: Garganacl will rub its fingertips together and sprinkle injured Pokémon with salt. Even severe wounds will promptly heal afterward.

name: Charcadet
pokedex: Burnt charcoal came to life and became a Pokémon. Possessing a fiery fighting spirit, Charcadet will battle even tough opponents.

name: Armarouge
pokedex: This Pokémon clads itself in armor that has been fortified by fire energy, and it shoots blazing fireballs.

name: Ceruledge
pokedex: The fiery blades on its arms burn fiercely with the lingering resentment of a sword wielder who fell before accomplishing their goal.

name: Shroodle
pokedex: A mellow Pokémon, it keeps enemies away from its territory by painting markings around its nest using an acrid, poisonous liquid.

name: Lemural
pokedex: The color of the poisonous saliva depends on what the Pokémon eats. Lemural covers its fingers in its saliva and draws patterns on trees in forests.

name: Bramblin
pokedex: A soul unable to move on to the afterlife was blown around by the wind until it got tangled up with dried grass and became a Pokémon.

name: Brambleghast
pokedex: It will open the branches of its head to envelop its prey. Once it absorbs all the life energy it needs, it expels the prey and discards it.

name: Capsakid
pokedex: The more sunlight this Pokémon bathes in, the more spicy chemicals are produced by its body, and thus the spicier its moves become.

name: Scovillain
pokedex: The red head converts spicy chemicals into fire energy and blasts the surrounding area with a super spicy stream of flame.

name: Scaraglob
pokedex: It rolls its pristine snow ball around to stimulate life energy. It treasures its ball more than its own life.

name: Reincarab
pokedex: There is some kind of miraculous life essence inside its snow globe. Day and night, Reincarab rolls this globe soothingly with its legs.

name: Flittle
pokedex: Flittle's toes levitate about half an inch above the ground because of the psychic power emitted from the frills on the Pokémon's belly.

name: Espathra
pokedex: It emits psychic power from the gaps between its multicolored frills and sprints at speeds greater than 120 mph.

name: Tinkatink
pokedex: It swings its handmade hammer around to protect itself, but the hammer is often stolen by Pokémon that eat metal.

name: Tinkatuff
pokedex: This Pokémon will attack groups of Pawniard and Bisharp, gathering metal from them in order to create a large and sturdy hammer.

name: Tinkaton
pokedex: This intelligent Pokémon has a very daring disposition. It knocks rocks into the sky with its hammer, aiming for flying Corviknight.

name: Bombirdier
pokedex: Bombirdier eats minerals, the byproducts of which are processed and then stored in its chest apron. When it has a full payload, watch out!

name: Finizen
pokedex: It likes playing with others of its kind using the water ring on its tail. It uses ultrasonic waves to sense the emotions of other living creatures.

name: Palafin
pokedex: This Pokémon can change into an alter ego if it hears its allies calling for help, but will never show anybody its moment of transformation.

name: Varoom
pokedex: It is said that this Pokémon was born when an unknown poison Pokémon entered and inspirited an engine left at a scrap-processing factory.

name: Revavroom
pokedex: It creates a gas out of poison and minerals. It then detonates the gas in its cylinders--now numbering eight--to generate energy.

name: Cyclizar
pokedex: Apparently Cyclizar has been allowing people to ride on its back since ancient times. Depictions of this have been found in 10,000-year-old murals.

name: Glimmet
pokedex: It absorbs minerals, but isn't good at regulating its internal energy. If overloaded, it will discharge deadly energy beams.

name: Glimmora
pokedex: Glimmora's petals are made of crystallized energy. In battle, it will open these up and fire beams from its conical body.

name: Greavard
pokedex: This Pokémon is undyingly vigilant and obedient. Its reliable candle lights up while on duty after being given an order.

name: Barroward
pokedex: Barroward spends most of its time keeping watch in graveyards with only its head protuberance exposed. Among all Pokémon, this one is most loyal.

name: Cetoddle
pokedex: This species left the ocean and began living on land a very long time ago. It seems to be closely related to Wailmer.

name: Cetitan
pokedex: Ice energy builds up in the horn on its upper jaw, causing the horn to reach cryogenic temperatures that freeze its surroundings.

name: Annihilape
pokedex: When its anger rose beyond a critical point, this Pokémon gained power that is unfettered by the limits of its physical body.

name: Farigiraf
pokedex: The hardened head from the tail protects the head of the main body as Farigiraf whips its long neck around to headbutt enemies.

name: Kingambit
pokedex: Only a Bisharp that stands above all others in its vast army can evolve into Kingambit.

name: Frigibax
pokedex: Using the power of its energy-storing dorsal fin, Frigibax cools the inside of its nest like a refrigerator.

name: Arctibax
pokedex: Arctibax freezes the air around it, protecting its face with an ice mask and turning its dorsal fin into a blade of ice.

name: Excelsius
pokedex: It launches itself into battle by flipping upside down and spewing frigid air from its mouth. It finishes opponents off with its dorsal blade.

name: Gimmigoon
pokedex: This Pokémon was born inside a treasure chest about 1,500 years ago. It sucks the life-force out of scoundrels who try to steal the treasure.

name: Smoliv
pokedex: It protects itself from enemies by emitting oil from its head. This oil is bitter and astringent enough to make someone flinch.

name: Dolliv
pokedex: Dolliv shares its tasty, fresh-scented oil with others. This species has coexisted with humans since times long gone.

name: Arboliva
pokedex: This calm Pokémon is very compassionate. It drives back enemies by launching its rich, aromatic oil at them with enough force to smash boulders.

name: Wo-Chien
pokedex: The grudge of a person punished for writing the king's evil deeds upon wooden tablets has clad itself in dead leaves to become a Pokémon.

name: Chien-Pao
pokedex: The hatred of those who perished by the sword long ago has clad itself in snow and become a Pokémon.

name: Ting-Lu
pokedex: The fear poured into an ancient ritual vessel has clad itself in rocks and dirt to become a Pokémon.

name: Chi-Yu
pokedex: The envy accumulated within curved beads that sparked multiple conflicts has clad itself in fire and become a Pokémon.

name: Koraidon
pokedex: This seems to be the Winged King mentioned in an old expedition journal. It was said to have split the land with its bare fists.

name: Miraidon
pokedex: Much remains unknown about this creature. It resembles Cyclizar, but it is far more ruthless and powerful.

name: GRD Scyther
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Regice. Its sharp glass body is seemingly unassailable.

name: GRD Hitmonlee
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Registeel. The elasticity of its body makes its actions highly irregular and unpredictable.

name: Obliveon
pokedex: What looks like bandages is actually part of an extended skeletal system. Its body requires maintenance to prevent it from decaying.

name: Papilleon
pokedex: It possesses 3 stomachs, a chitinous exoskeleton in addition to a bone skeleton, 2 small brains in its antennae, and 4 fashionable booties!

name: Titaneon
pokedex: Its futuristic skin has a built-in A.I. system that optimizes its muscular and cardio-vascular performance. There are occasional errors, however.

name: Vigilanteon
pokedex: It has unshakeable convictions. It yields to no one, and will not be reasoned with while pursuing what it believes must be done.

name: GRD Maushold
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Maushold? Or perhaps the dolls are vessels for wisdom, emotions, and willpower to awaken something greater...

name: Disembrain
pokedex: This Pokemon is mostly brain matter. It gets easily frustrated doing hard things and often falls back down to where it started.

name: Cerenoyum
pokedex: Stuck in its ways and quick to complain, it persists on. It grows increasingly frustrated that its dreams haven't yet come true.

name: Caffiend
pokedex: Finely ground, energetic, and always busy, it blows off steam with parts of its bean body as it runs contentiously from place to place.

name: H. Growlithe
pokedex: They stand vigilant watch over their craggy terraces, leading many to thinking they are statues. It contains igneous components in its head and tail tufts.

name: H. Arcanine
pokedex: Renowned as mighty dynastic guardians, they stand watch outside of palaces. They shed piles of soot from their impressive earthen bodies.

name: Avaterra
pokedex: It alters its capabilities depending on the terrain or surrounding conditions. It is supposedly full of untapped meta-energy.

name: Ogerpon
pokedex: This mischief-loving Pokémon is full of curiosity. It battles by drawing out the type-based energy contained within its masks.

name: GRD Empoleon
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Articuno. It carries a pristine and stately essence.

name: GRD Sableye
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Celebi. It appears to be able to possess time itself.

name: GRD Excadrill
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Moltres. It is hostile and temperamental.

name: Terrapagos
pokedex: It is more durable in this form, improving its terrain functionality. It constantly shimmers with multi-colored meta-energy.

name: GRD Deoxys

name: GRD Farfetch'd
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Zapdos. It streaks into combat with unmatched audacity.

name: Grizzerie
pokedex: Grizzerie will sleep for months in uliginous environments, its dreams somehow altering the surrounding ecosystem.

name: Hooplanex
pokedex: The most powerful Ultra Beast, it possesses the overwhelming avarice of its makers. If unleashed, it seizes anything it desires.

name: GRD Palossand
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Mew. It has absorbed enough genetic information to reproduce Pokemon life.

name: GRD Leafeon
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Shaymin. It blooms from loss with feelings of hope and goodwill.

name: GRD Pidgeot
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Entei. Parting the clouds as it descends, its very presence is godlike.

name: GRD Mismarrow
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Meloetta. It streaks into combat with unmatched audacity.

name: GRD Milotic
pokedex: A fallen Pokémon resurrected with the essence of Meloetta. It streaks into combat with unmatched audacity.
